In this bromance, the cinematic equivalent of a 
rom-com buddy flick, Paul Rudd plays a recently 
engaged guy who's got the bride-to-be of his 
dreams but lacks an all-important significant other 
when it comes to their pending nuptials: a best man. 
On a determined hunt for a stranger who will stand 
up for him, he eventually meets a candidate (Jason 
Segel) with wedding-party potential. Jaime Pressly, 
Rashida Jones and Jon Favreau co-star.

Starring: Paul Rudd, Jason Segel
